<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ReadSpark</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    header {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22c55e);
      color: white;
    }
    header h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
    header p { margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }

    section { padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: auto; }
    h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #020617;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    }

    .leaderboard table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .leaderboard th, .leaderboard td {
      padding: 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .leaderboard th { color: #22c55e; }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #020617;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>ReadSpark</h1>
  <p>Where reading becomes a challenge, a community, and a spark ğŸ”¥</p>
</header>

<section>
  <h2>What is ReadSpark?</h2>
  <p>
    ReadSpark is a digital platform built to make reading exciting, social, and rewarding.
    It combines books, articles, writing, and challenges into one space designed for students and young readers.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Core Features</h2>
  <div class="features">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>ğŸ“š Smart Reading</h3>
      <p>Track books, articles, and reading time automatically.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>ğŸ† Leaderboards</h3>
      <p>Compete weekly & monthly for most books read, reading streaks, and advanced reading levels.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>âœï¸ Writing Zone</h3>
      <p>Publish stories, essays, poems, and get community feedback.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>ğŸ– Badges & Rewards</h3>
      <p>Earn badges, streak bonuses, and exclusive ranks.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="leaderboard">
  <h2>Leaderboard Preview</h2>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>Rank</th>
      <th>User</th>
      <th>Books Read</th>
      <th>Streak</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>1</td>
