      <td>15 days</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Our Vision</h2>
  <p>
    ReadSpark aims to build a generation that reads not because they have to,
    but because they want to. By blending competition, creativity, and community,
    we turn reading into a lifestyle.
  </p>
</section>

